    <small>559-530 BC</small>
    "]
    ---
    Cyrus2["
    <small>538 BC</small>
    <small>Makes decree to rebuild the temple, thus fulfilling <b>Jeremiah's</b> prophecy of 70 years of exile.</small>
    "]
    ---
