    <small>552-486 BC</small>
    "]
    ---
    Darius2["
    <small>536 BC</small>
    <small>Stops the building of the temple based on a appeal from the people living in Samaria.</small>
    "]
    ---
    Darius3["
    <small>520 BC</small>
    <small><b>Haggai</b> and <b>Zechariah</b> prophesy, then <b>Zerubbabel</b> and <b>Jeshua</b> continue the temple construction. Darius allows this when he is reminded of Cyrus' decree.</small>
    "]
    ---
    Darius4["
    <small>515 BC</small>
